---
title: Cheesy Double Plant-Based Mince Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa
description: Smokey, cheesy, and packed with flavour, these quesadillas are a total crowd-pleaser! Stuffed with saucy, spiced double veggie mince and melty cheese, then crisped to golden perfection, they’re pure comfort with a twist. On the side? A bright, zesty charred corn salsa that brings the perfect pop of sweetness and crunch. Get ready for a hands-on, flavour-loaded fiesta!
